_sText:
bhop_toc is an easy to medium level map with 3 different themes. I made it with a dedication to my friend Toc' :D
Hope you will like it, it took me a good while to create it :)

Music: Emil Berliner - Flummifreuden / 
       Oxia - Domino / 
       Crash Bandicoot 1 - Theme / 
       Crash Bandicoot 3 - Warped - Theme
